About:
__

Adapted by Adrian Bean

When Jess Tyler's two-timing wife left him he stayed on at the farm alone, growing corn and going to Church. Nearly twenty years later, a young woman turns up with a suitcase, and there's an immediate attraction between them. The problem is that the young woman is Jess's daughter, Kady. Or is she? Only the butterfly birthmark can settle the question for good. A tale of revenge, murder and forbidden love.

CAST
Jess Tyler - John Chancer
Kady - Ashleigh Haddad
Wash - Solomon Mousley

Deputy - Martin T Sherman

Directed by Kate McAll
